# LifeOS — Project Vision

## What this is

A **Personal Life Operating System** — a React Native + Expo mobile app that accepts
voice or text input, uses AI to classify and route information into 5 structured
domains, sends smart reminders, and generates a personalized morning briefing.

Built first for Abhishek (personal use, June 2026), designed to scale into a product
and eventually a plugin platform under ennoble.ai.

**This is NOT a to-do app.** It is personal infrastructure — the AI-powered
equivalent of a personal assistant available 24/7, including at 2am.

---

## Mission: Enabling the Noble

Primary target: someone in Tier 2/3 India — same life complexity as anyone (health,
work, family, learning, ideas, finance) but without the organizational tools that
privileged people have access to.

Every design decision must pass this test:
**Does this work on a mid-range Android, with patchy internet, for someone more
comfortable speaking Hindi than typing English?**

---

## The 5 Domains

Everything the user says or types routes into one of these:

| Domain | What it is | Signal words |
|--------|-----------|--------------|
| `health` | Medicine, daily habits, recurring body routines | medicine, dose, daily, habit |
| `task` | Actionable items, one-time or recurring, errands | do, fix, repair, call, buy, book |
| `learning` | Skills, courses, long-term knowledge goals | learn, study, course, skill, practice |
| `idea` | Concepts, product seeds, "what if" thoughts | idea, what if, build, imagine, create |
| `note` | Ephemeral context facts (auto-expire 24h) | remember that, FYI, keys, location |

Default: if uncertain → `task`. Short context-only text with no action → `note`.

---

## MVP Features (what we are building now)

1. Universal Inbox — speak or type anything, AI classifies and routes
2. Voice capture — expo-av → Whisper transcription → classify
3. Health reminders — medicine 3×/day push notifications, habit streaks
4. Tasks — one-time, recurring, ephemeral (auto-expire), priority
5. Learning goals — spaced repetition, session log, streaks
6. Idea seeds — flagged for future IdeaBox (no research in MVP)
7. Morning briefing — AI narrative pushed at 7am, covers all domains
8. 2am brain dump — frictionless late-night voice capture, processed in morning
9. AI chat — "What should I focus on today?", natural language queries
10. Anti-entropy — weekly AI review surfaces stale/avoided entries

---

## Future: Plugin Platform (design toward this, don't build it yet)

Core = Inbox + AI Router + Reminder Engine + Morning Briefing
Plugins = MedTracker, IdeaBox, Finance OS, Learning Tracker, Travel Agent

Each plugin works standalone OR integrates with core via plugin API.
Write domain logic in isolated files/hooks now — the architecture emerges from this.
